gree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我估黃之鋒三個月教導所出返黎<br />\n<br />\n佢都可以揪死解放軍"},{"pid":"fa179ce4878978017532f409a52ac0fd1fc52552","tid":373932,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"掃唔到街無所謂<br />\n最緊要嗰隻雞！你救到未？"},{"pid":"4ca5f2e274df1363f06696334191a4e3e44c5f29","tid":373932,"uid":4931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:39:47.000Z","msg":"清潔工啲厭惡工作，真係要提高啲人工先合理。"},{"pid":"791c3ecb90cfb3d5aa4b5ae65eb93696d606bf91","tid":373932,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解嗰啲軍服同抗日膠劇咁似嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佛山片場老臨，跟霞姐架，有幾件仲拍過超時空男臣，成百蚊日架。"},{"pid":"f2c53f832a534356b19df9003a73318af981d8cf","tid":373932,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該係暑假搵啲軍事訓練營果啲中學生嚟頂，跟手收番阿公一大筆錢。<br />\n<br />\n呢班學生仲要係俾錢參加個訓練營。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要加入解放軍, 就要用錢收買軍官<br />\n所以能夠做到解放軍既人, 都係屋企有小小錢既少爺仔<br />\n<br />\n所以解放軍就係咁, 一班少爺兵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢班係班有錢少爺兵去中學請番嚟嘅替工嚟架，果班少爺兵又點會肯幫你執垃圾。"},{"pid":"054cc16cf5204bc68ed2a685fe478386643cc713","tid":373932,"uid":7190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:47:41.000Z","msg":"有兩條五毛比左負皮"},{"pid":"a04a30dc73ad37915285151f0f1729fa59b6ebfe","tid":373932,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有兩條五毛比左負皮</blockquote><br />\n2個澳門人"},{"pid":"95e8f034b806001e5c8317be0a169847cf932bf0","tid":373932,"uid":4850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:48:50.000Z","msg":"這是正宗錄用的解放軍嗎"},{"pid":"677bb5925787814880abf842d99d8d04b2f77db1","tid":373932,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:50:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b96cbcac9b53a472f43dc07